channel.title: Nobiwascape v3
channel.description:
ive made a new server a 508 server
it's based on espeon.
i renamed some files like src to server and that shit
features: almost full fishing u get random a fish not always u need the levels for fishing: only some eels doest work do it later
click on varrock teleport u will be teled to the dragon dungeon: there is a baby blue,green.blue,red,kingblack,mithril dragon in there
home teleport works only need to add the emotes.
added one clue scroll u need to use items on it u get a package than use another thing on it and u got something use it with the key and use the key on the chest to get a random reward
ogre teleport u to kqueen, godwars full working all npc's only need to add some normal bandos npc's in his lair, working on npc vs npc in there sometimes the mage will attack a where wolf.
specials working on npc and player.
working on herblore now.
full kq lair u will be teled in the place where u use the rope on the hle in the dessert
than u can climb down.
there is the kqueen she has 2 forms whn the first1 is dead the other one comes.
full bone burry.
almost full thieving
got full cooking of the fish use the fish on the fire in the hole
almost full warrior guild.
almsot all npc's drop stuff
base set off wc

more pics coming soon
i hope you like it
